POST /v1/transactions/{businessTransactionId}/executions

GET /v1/transactions/{businessTransactionId}/executions/{executionId}


Locked architectural decision
status is the only execution state field.
Valid values are:
PROCESSING
COMPLETED
FAILED
There is no separate outcome field.
Execution success or failure is determined solely from status.

This keeps the API aligned with the locked Execution Lifecycle Model and avoids duplicate state.

